- Smoothing: use EMA for \\(w_\{ij\}, \\tau_\{ij\}, P\\) to avoid thrash; decay factor \\(\\gamma \\in [0.7,0.95]\\).  \
- Thresholds: learn \\(\\lambda,\\tau^\\*,\\tau_\{tc\}\\) from replay; provide safe defaults and per-sector overrides (core/peripheral/transitional/deep).  \
